      "message": "Patch Set 1: Verified+1\n\nPassed enforced test review-ldiskfs-dne on CentOS 7.0/x86_64 uploaded by Trevis Autotest2 from trevis-50vm1: https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/f21c8d4d-a274-4fed-a8de-6468a3fb29d3 ran 5 tests.",
